The paper deals with coding theory and quantum coding theory, which are closely related to information theory (cs.IT). The focus is on MDS codes, which are a topic in algebraic coding theory (cs.GT). The paper also involves constructing families of codes, which could fall under the category of discrete structures (cs.DS). The application of the codes to quantum error correction suggests a connection to control theory (cs.SY) and quantum information (cs.QI).
